<br>
In the speech community that is EQ, 'donation' is coming to mean 'fee'.<br>
<br>
That's all there is to it, imo. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.studioeternity.com/EverquestFV/Viala02.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
