<br>
*bonks Zaith* <br>
<br>
I had a discussion about temp tonight.  In the last 5 LDoN groups I asked if the cost of the peridots could be taken off the top before split.  I have been met with silence or oh sure. . .but surprisingly they always forget.  Now figure, it cost me 66pp in peridots per group and to do a dungeon the cleric needs KEI.  I donate 50pp for it.  So each group is costing me 116pp.  Most splits are about 60-80pp.  You do the math.  I have even stopped leveling my cleric simple because I can't afford spells.  I have done the casting temp for 20pp in order to get enough to purchase KEI before a group and more peridots.  <br>
<br>
Tonight I made the decision to either cast only heroism on the group or stop doing LDoN.  I simply can't continue to afford it.  Want clerics to stop &quot;whoring&quot; themselves?  Then have groups put a crowbar in their wallets and pay for the buff or do without.  <br>
<br>
Of the 31 LDoN I have done only 4 have covered the cost of the dots out of the group loot before split and a few individuals within the group.  Always the same ones.  Those I remember and this was in no way directed at them.  It is just becoming a pain and if I must do without a group because I won't cast then so be it.  When you get to where you can cast temp Zaith I think your going to understand a bit more why clerics have had to start selling this buff.<br>
<br>
Dessirra <br>
